WEBVTT

00:10.013 --> 00:11.948
(exclaiming)

00:16.286 --> 00:18.254
(school bell ringing)

00:20.891 --> 00:21.924
(Barney belches)

00:21.959 --> 00:24.227
(tires screeching)

00:24.261 --> 00:25.595
D'oh!

00:25.629 --> 00:27.196
(tires screeching)

00:27.231 --> 00:28.831
(grunts)

00:36.306 --> 00:37.707
(groaning)

00:37.741 --> 00:40.376
(laughs)

00:40.401 --> 00:44.401
<font color="#00FF00">♪ The Simpsons 25x07 ♪</font>
<font color="#00FFFF">Yellow Subterfuge</font>
